Description: n R package for collecting, processing, and visualizing Internet infrastructure data 
    from DBIP (https://db-ip.com/). The package provides automated tools to download IP geolocation 
    and Autonomous System (ASN) data, transform it into tidy formats, and create interactive 
    dashboards for analyzing Internet topology and global connectivity patterns. Key features 
    include data scraping and ETL pipelines, quatro-based web applications with geographic 
    visualizations, and containerized deployment via Docker.
